7\. Key Learnings

6.  Haiku 4.5 max_tokens 8192 is a hard ceiling. Prompts requesting 15+
    structured items with URLs will truncate. Keep output budget under
    7000 tokens.

7.  Docker container name is \'postgres\', not \'corpfit_postgres\'.
    Update any scripts referencing the old name.

8.  cloudflared runs as a local Windows process (cloudflared tunnel run
    n8n-corpfit), not as a Docker container. Must be started manually
    after reboot.

9.  Unicode arrows (↗️ ↑ →) are technically emoji in Unicode but should
    be treated as professional formatting on LinkedIn. Gate 3 v2.1
    whitelists them.

10. PowerShell double-quote escaping breaks with psql -c for multi-line
    SQL. Use here-strings (@\"\...\"@) piped to docker exec -i instead.

